Package: soilprofile2
Type: Package
Title: Visualisation of Soilprofile
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gabriel Holz
Maintainer: The package maintainer <gabriholz@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions to graphically represent 
	     soil properties. Morphological data gathered in the field 
	     such as horizon boundaries, root abundance and dimensions,
	     skeletal shape, abundance and dimension as well as	
	     meaningful soil color may be represented via the plot
	     function. Different layers were disignd with the new SF packager, 
	     and plottet with ggplot2.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Depends: tidyverse, sf, smoothr
Imports: tidyverse, sf, smoothr, aqp
Suggests: tidyverse, sf

